Class RowGameController

  • java.lang.Object
    • controller.RowGameController

  • public class RowGameController
extends java.lang.Object
    Violation 4 - MVC Architecture RowGameController is the controller between model and view. Changes that are received from view are being propagated to the model and vice versa.
